{"hd07dbb82g3f5dg48f9gad48g6a6065aacbc8": ["Why you succulent schemer! You promised meat, but offer nary a scrap!", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "fae2cf29-ebb3-b49a-44cd-98905598cb18"], "h36690cc6ged4fg4671g9900g30738420ab49": ["Good thing I've a hankering for <i>horns.</i>", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "83cdc931-cb1b-dfe9-989b-5c0f463f233c"], "hda75bb7fgae42g4ab2ga8b8g82fd1b4c77cf": ["But I know <i>just</i> the thing to sate my appetite.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "83cdc931-cb1b-dfe9-989b-5c0f463f233c"], "hb756a205g8c98g42b4gb986g2b91e6beca1f": ["No more than a few pecks? I'm afraid this spread is most inadequate.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "e8e62629-6a13-f699-b349-081575deb13a"], "hf76d2d0cgeffeg4a31gaa6cg5bcd033cfc43": ["Our bargain is at an end - unless, perhaps, you've a spicier deal?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "05311856-65d7-a280-6a2b-5a2b546b156f"], "h1065e8e5g494ag494eg8a72g0c0af982e6fc": ["If you'll help me in another battle, I'll pay ([6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "c7491f55-1b12-7cba-5674-d0235bffb41c"], "h07caa692gc849g4300ga40ag415e5b4d52db": ["A fine offer - we are back in business.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "026bbd31-df3a-805b-ef72-a729a958e76c"], "h6e3eb4b1g3da0g4c1egbfeeg2be067038922": ["You know my terms. Sound the horn when you are ready.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "7d47807e-80eb-3a50-fa1e-58f5a0e22992"], "hf1d78e5agf59ag4de6g849ege85ba96ac4f5": ["Our deal is done. I wish you well.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "7fb6e7eb-8e0c-afb6-dd4d-429f6ae726e1"], "h203a8ac9gcc93g4027gb498ga4bd0fe1488a": ["Without so much as a lick of that mouth-watering meat of yours?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "c346a87e-e06e-243f-5833-d3c290bbc9cd"], "hd18f5563g2317g4081ga78cg4cb7588cfe31": ["Not even a lick.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "9ea513a0-af73-c36c-61b5-b1e416d63761"], "hd80235b4g7f06g4b4dga213gb43cb7643919": ["A pity for us both. Until later.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "79e61780-9543-5b36-d0a7-47e7f23b8899"], "heb12df6dg874dg4a17g99a7gdfd7f352b335": ["Fine. One lick.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "1c2f87d5-ff9a-d821-005f-708eabe5134c"], "h280437feg2bb8g4324ga361gd55f913762fa": ["Consider me satisfied.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "0d0fc1c4-ad38-86cc-1db1-12c8d56110be"], "h348790c0gd821g40e9ga24eg6e57337170cc": ["I'll pay generously - after the next fight. ([463b0f43-5410-412d-aba3-875cf81c38ca])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "d72cb17d-2893-833b-e517-9dac39ea02e0"], "h19a63ce5gab69g4ae1g9f69g6bc654c2dbc6": ["A fine offer - we are back in business.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "b814e2f3-d23b-ab98-0d5c-df895f3a8987"], "h473eaee5g186eg4d4bgb0c6gefaef94ebc89": ["Come now - an ogre feasts not on promises.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "0ea0a168-e5af-2835-89e1-23682632ba04"], "h9058386bg395dg40f2gb269g8f3de50cd1d0": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "b44589e1-1a41-6c49-bba7-eb1fbcabec07"], "h3e5ada03ga3e8g44f5g8ebfgb43ab7cfba5b": ["<i>Delicious!</i>", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "d318a289-5f1a-5c1d-0843-025ee002ff9d"], "hc6f7da9dgab75g4512g9ac8g3b9513776d03": ["The deal is done.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "de95e861-2c39-22a3-5512-e0d8ecdc9a62"], "hfd81fc28g3528g40cbga3cdgfb215b1f8153": ["Now pay up.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "7443e1c3-0db0-7d6c-3ac4-b626c8d2199e"], "h85811d22gf475g4ea8g9490gb5f74a1d8e94": ["You didn't even kill anyone!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "fa567c38-9319-c80e-14cc-d7050221089b"], "hc63e32fdg0da8g4883g81a9g429854ff8ced": ["You summon, you pay. That's the bargain.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "31aa5f99-3c0a-883d-3416-ab1ff15895bf"], "ha676fdf9g4e7fg40bdg9015g21492ee62a88": ["What use does an ogre have for gold?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "e65d437a-f42c-1cf7-b684-276030d480bd"], "he0342765gaee9g4fd6gb739gab190e883203": ["Is gold not the pilot of our world-vessel? I am a proud glutton - and not just for meat.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "4a2d5fe5-092d-8320-d6d4-ea1ca8681d31"], "h125c3dd0g90b0g4f01ga84cgd683bdc6662a": ["<i>Pay what you promised. ([463b0f43-5410-412d-aba3-875cf81c38ca])</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "881c6248-3509-d19e-302b-d059024aaa81"], "hc30b5d37gc5e4g4caag868fg10ddd8165f37": ["You didn't think this through, did you?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "203480b8-6f1c-85a9-f887-b38ee7825751"], "h6e691122gef7fg4828g98d5g5996ae66f596": ["Well I'll be. I almost expected you to back out of our bargain.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "a2d72417-5701-ea38-2067-3cd3fd689a84"], "he4fc8dffg7344g4183g9828gea1dc521f35c": ["Yet I'm afraid I've but one last battle in me. Shall we renew our contract once more?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "c07d0356-30ab-39e9-65fc-d5f96d57f52a"], "h0cdaef58g5aeag4198gaf06g0717db51a258": ["Instead, I propose a renewal. What say you?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "da9d994f-5ca1-6215-ce22-ad67e7d9fb5d"], "hc9c4bd6bg4763g475cgb32eg1a63b1f41dff": ["All right. I'll pay now, and you come when I call. ([6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "9eec3466-e76c-9efc-c1f4-28bbeb74fc63"], "hd84fd6d8g641fg4529g8ea8gdbac20fb098a": ["Consider it a deal, my morsel.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "3643dc67-3d77-4d7a-4a55-1fe3017aafe0"], "hba3a15a8gd50ag4b24g9610gbd9f402aefaf": ["All right. I'll pay now, and you come when I call. ([6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "2353470f-5792-7183-631d-209d4ba28c40"], "h4bd22b54g2789g44d1gbc18g5afee3d4fcbd": ["Agreed. You'll be paid for another battle - <i>after</i> it's done. ([5dac5eea-faeb-459c-b675-46c51519b784])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "b6c603de-d113-3aa4-5bbc-39478af4c06b"], "h1d62145eg7338g4428ga372g20b5a375edcd": ["I have no words...", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "77b38fbb-bea4-fc2d-01e2-0dcbe7ff1838"], "h2a378d50g306bg42a6gb07bgf12b1b6d62c0": ["Oh-ho! I appreciate your zeal - but I think we've all learned a lesson here about <i>risk</i>, yes?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "f8e92f8c-2460-587a-7921-49fe666e4c7c"], "h356e7659g92beg48f8g9abegd8912c9984c0": ["Really? I mean - really?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "9889878b-02a7-d908-0b66-052ab3a93d83"], "h83577a8bgfe28g438bgae35gd2d829a55ffa": ["No. Our deal is done.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "68488795-014e-2c39-1c1f-6e3c83addf25"], "hb19c34d4g6b18g4b15ga87bga1b209d768a6": ["It's as I feared. You've lost your senses.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "5b6c5a84-4aa6-4d4b-8669-b3cdd21998ef"], "hc2cc3117g587ag488egad87g8e7666d9654f": ["*Reality dawns. You've been outsmarted by an ogre.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "8d9b635d-5c27-db4c-3245-a19849380437"], "h02f01b1eg6aa3g4471g91b3g79e01fef3701": ["I don't have your money.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "d106f27d-beca-c7d1-006f-411daf6d2106"], "h38b620bbgaedbg4130g864bg5336076cf13b": ["Why you succulent schemer! Good thing I've a hankering for <i>horns.</i>", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "235a50d6-ecd8-4061-4c15-ba93703ff2b2"], "hbc08fddfg7583g4996gbe16gc0d73673e984": ["Why you succulent schemer! I know <i>just</i> the thing to sate my appetite.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "235a50d6-ecd8-4061-4c15-ba93703ff2b2"], "ha181ea9eg20fdg4144gad2dgff8c05afed29": ["Have patience. The spoils of the next battle will be far greater. ([01f129ea-b4dc-44b6-8154-9a948f876a82])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "a7a0201e-e817-d0e0-18ee-5cd28b4e94ad"], "hf250fa7dg5096g4da6g99fbge6ba6c433596": ["You've got my mouth watering. We are agreed, morsel.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "79f7c4ea-f7c4-d6c8-2244-bb08151888e9"], "h8305313eg3c15g45b2ga526g07b21edaa057": ["Too good to be true, my morsel. Now pay up.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "ebead2c0-0df7-51ab-9542-27ad503c7398"], "h190f2b68g3c68g45c7g8482ge49a18dd7aa7": ["<i>Attack the ogre.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "93ce23a2-0dba-6d5c-5ac6-4bb9bd480657"], "h2dc63221g80cag4411g94f8g26bcdb82aa73": ["The deal is done. ", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "baaf82ce-b523-6a70-f3f5-c6963093d4ee"], "h1ffd4631g41a2g4be1g92ddg7298eb804161": ["Shall we extend our contract?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "c80325a2-800e-ffe6-d0e1-2746809a18ee"], "h7d73aca6g72b5g4025g9c34g1e70f9660642": ["Lets. Take this and be ready when I call again. ([6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "b4bcbc02-d9ef-caf5-99ff-4abbaa146d16"], "h332b235agd5fbg4467g8414g14f5fab1c3f3": ["That's that, then. Let's see the gold.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "5d717983-adb3-845b-39c4-45e2e9400aa9"], "hed32a2d0g0dd2g4f43g8f0bg569e5161a9d8": ["<i>Pay what you promised. ([01f129ea-b4dc-44b6-8154-9a948f876a82])</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "7002798f-84ef-8f10-ed39-bd59a9ffc4a1"], "h3a538342g3f2eg4a93g93a1g6e9e5c1baa1b": ["You didn't think this through, did you?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "8de433aa-4bcf-df0d-1844-c45e10631ab3"], "h9b429c07g4589g42fbg9319gae634bf07bb0": ["Well I'll be. I almost expected you to back out of our bargain.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "32d5a1cb-c09f-8336-fea7-70cedf46f882"], "ha1a99862gf6eag4c5egb57cge277e8d7bb59": ["I'm afraid I've but one last battle in me. Shall we renew our contract once more?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "2a4a966c-d6ad-4c94-6925-926aa43752a8"], "h9be26336g38a6g4d8fg89d1g7c33e2b41edf": ["Fine. Your fee now, to fight for me when I call. ([6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "6f19ee66-1bca-8d14-9de0-dcfead0d500d"], "h3a594052g9befg4f5fgad32g1c3e20fabe00": ["A fine agreement, my morsel!", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "107bd19b-3de7-ffc5-89be-5aa87b68149f"], "h3f3fda26g908bg46c9gb677g942ef0539f24": ["I'll increase your fee - to be paid <i>after </i>the next fight. ([5dac5eea-faeb-459c-b675-46c51519b784])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "0dd380b6-3ed0-845a-e968-0cb66b84ec4f"], "hfa47a357gc5cfg4bf9g86cfg4cb271da3b03": ["I have no words...", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "cd272e04-cd44-5926-b2d3-8624f15bdf89"], "h54377e12g684dg4746gacb6g72db034ce48e": ["Oh-ho! I appreciate your zeal - but I think we've all learned a lesson here about <i>risk</i>, yes?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "5a4844da-3af4-9522-0ef0-39873df29bb6"], "hb453cec7g0e64g4b9eg9280ga48c5723f957": ["Really? I mean - really?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "baa91ce5-b9e7-6173-29d3-f5f8fd4ed7bd"], "h93a23360g208cg47b1gb708gbafb455aad22": ["No, our deal's done.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "7c90aeba-c833-874c-c65c-7bde487a58c9"], "h77bb255fge72eg4254g8d70g34e9293ed7f5": ["It's as I feared. You've lost your senses.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "76a95bd6-72b6-674f-83c5-20a3283f0c12"], "h9f6b83a2g1560g458dg8f2dg8ae32ddb3444": ["*Reality dawns. You've been outsmarted by an ogre.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "bf50bc95-2412-1cee-60cf-39b4b8810500"], "h50641739gaddbg4f54g8bbeg81e116a68917": ["My battles aren't done. Hold out until the next, and it'll be worth your while. ([5dac5eea-faeb-459c-b675-46c51519b784])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "8afca9c5-db44-cdaa-beaf-cfda0aaece4d"], "h9dc60a1agaf65g4478g9f76g00018e286f5b": ["Indeed? A risky bargain - but one I must accept.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "f05f1eab-d948-f035-bb4e-b2cc6406db01"], "h67ca8701g24a1g4959g8247g3fd5382cf2a8": ["I'm calling your bluff. Pay up. <i>Now.</i>", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "957d3cb9-15f1-e719-0b89-7b2a18e1682b"], "h0bc38043g1ff7g4c9fg9930gada7e08e35d2": ["That's that, then. ", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "8ea9c30b-0463-7d95-6f48-6768d25a3646"], "h118ba875g01e6g45bcga32cga751cb057587": ["Let's see the gold.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "6ec91c20-f108-b230-2d0a-0fd23cbf36d9"], "h4904f570gf44eg4085gadcdg5b78145318f5": ["Well that's that! I've but one last battle in me. ", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "33e7eeb3-e24c-8ad7-1da0-642a9f021da9"], "h444dc1eage94dg4a06gaa9dg0d8be981d18e": ["Shall we extend our bargain?", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "8b324e33-45b6-4dde-3af3-3bbdc740ad3e"], "hc047ff6agf4aeg44b5gaffeg5087144105cc": ["Agreed. I'll have need of you again. ([6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54] gold.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "a4b1c007-00b2-f1ce-5771-f394d473f3c6"], "h3889b336gfe6ag4e1cg9e6fgb15222a1ca87": ["A feast for the ages, then!", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "4a9532db-38b7-bd24-9fab-e6b5978a4481"], "hdfea1e86ge8e1g45abgbd12g81887eb73635": ["Call when you're ready, my morsel - and not a <i>moment</i> before.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "bd7cc95d-ddc2-8a1a-816a-ad88c735edc7"], "h47a6d4dbg5e3bg4674g8232gf069b34ed0b2": ["I've done my part.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "40fdbb7f-ad4f-c2bb-2bba-db476e7b45d0"], "hd182449bg4996g40bag9766gf6d54dc4f982": ["<i>Now show me the gold.</i>", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "3fc6f7f7-9b75-bdcc-b01d-dc2ac3dddc00"], "h8d5cbab7g1d61g4464g9c7ag3ae0fb4bdd62": ["<i>Pay what you promised. ([5dac5eea-faeb-459c-b675-46c51519b784])</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "48e7d932-d592-7762-704c-c4dddb2a1f4b"], "hab511ea0g1097g4923gbfeeg9789fa9f0ccc": ["You didn't think this through, did you?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "f9902206-615f-d175-5086-f0d8c053b3e4"], "hc3f20764g3f69g47caga0dcg62bb82840308": ["It was an absolute <i>pleasure</i> doing business.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "a5989cbc-4a1e-2a4b-7a8d-a56d34da7b18"], "hfc4b59cag32e7g46e1ga006g15b19c585722": ["How about a lick of that mouth-watering meat of yours. A parting gift, as it were.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "d77cf9d4-ca77-a67a-6e77-6a773afbefb8"], "h00e8a436gce34g4527g9a1eg168351681fa5": ["It's as I feared. You've lost your senses.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "204dbadd-443c-f033-ca86-e1339b3d1a78"], "h038688cegb287g4fe9g900bg254ee73362ee": ["*Reality hits. You've been outsmarted by an ogre.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "b5244057-4ec9-2600-29b2-bbf1a607d26b"], "h4449a385g1602g4663ga7efg37c487c3ac75": ["<i>Attack the ogre.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "9d702771-b2d4-ceba-dc07-37515bd97250"], "hc3ad9094gc1abg4254ga76eg2d07707496bd": ["So our terms have concluded, my little morsel. But there's one last favour I might ask:", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "88989e97-a2a7-395d-477f-4779755a7ee6"], "h7888536ega614g4585gb123g4c567aff26c1": ["A lick of that mouth-watering meat of yours. A parting gift, as it were.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_SchoolOgres_AfterSummon.html", "0d617de3-5768-2fad-3aea-b4c519abac3b"]}